Description: This package is used to work with weather data from the
    weather station network of the Ngorongoro Hyena Project.
    This package is mostly designed for advanced users that want to use
    the weather data for analyses.
    For a general summary of weather conditions in Ngorongoro Crater
    please see our reports (URL).
    For a clean subset of the data summarised by day please see our
    summary data (URL).
